author: szetszwo
msg: HDFS-2527. WebHdfs: remove the use of "Range" header in Open; use ugi username if renewer parameter is null in GetDelegationToken; response OK when setting replication for non-files; rename GETFILEBLOCKLOCATIONS to GET_BLOCK_LOCATIONS and state that it is a private unstable API; replace isDirectory and isSymlink with enum {FILE, DIRECTORY, SYMLINK} in HdfsFileStatus JSON object.
